    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "One other way to bypass (get excluded by the report) it is to add a function prefixed with `test` in the contract. That way forge thinks it's a test contract and don't have it on the list.\r\n\r\n```solidity\r\n\r\n// add this to be excluded from coverage report\r\nfunction test() public {}\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\nWorks for me for those mocks or tester contracts I don't really care. \r\n",
